TURNER v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND HOUSE OF CORRECTION [App. No. 29,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided October 23, 1964.

Before Henderson, C. J., and Hammond, Prescott, HornEy and Sybert, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons assigned in the opinion of Judge Evans in the court below.

Application denied.
